# Keep the Docker build context small + the image build hermetic.
target/
connector/target/
clients/**/target/
.git/
**/*.md
# EXCEPT markdown that is COMPILED IN via include_str! — excluding it breaks `cargo build`
# inside the image (the host toolchain never notices; only the docker context is filtered).
!crates/growlerdb-mcp/src/query_syntax.md
deploy/compose/seed/
# UI is built inside the image (node stage); don't ship the local deps/output.
**/node_modules
ui/dist
